      <li parentName="ul"><em parentName="li">{`On iOS: Open the `}<strong parentName="em">{`Settings`}</strong>{` app, tap `}<strong parentName="em">{`PagerDuty`}</strong>{`, then turn the `}<strong parentName="em">{`Reset`}</strong>{` toggle to the on position.`}</em>{` `}</li>
