##Not Receiving Push Notifications
Google Play Services must be enabled in order to receive push notifications on your Android device. If Google Play Services are enabled and the `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/docs/notification-troubleshooting#section-general-push-notification-troubleshooting-guide"
